# Dementia App Workspace

This workspace currently includes the mobile app in `apps/mobile`.

## Start the mobile app

1. Open a terminal in `Dementia App/apps/mobile`
2. Run:

```bash
npm install
npm start
```

## Main documentation

- Mobile app docs: `Dementia App/apps/mobile/README.md`
- QA checklist: `Dementia App/apps/mobile/QA.md`
- Handoff summary: `Dementia App/apps/mobile/HANDOFF_SUMMARY.md`

## Copy style (quick summary)

- Use plain labels and short button text.
- Keep one primary action per screen when possible.
- Use calm, supportive wording and avoid technical UI terms.

